src:
They said what?! Pros react to Corey Anderson’s TKO of Johnny Walker at UFC 244
03 Nov 2019, 01:52 by Lucas Rezende



Johnny Walker is no longer undefeated in the Octagon. In the first round of their bout at UFC 244, Corey Anderson rocked the Brazilian with a hard punch and never allowed his opponent to recover, picking up a TKO win shortly afterwards. On Twitter, pro fighters reacted to the fight.
